classitems.description: Creates a new appointment based on the given `options`.
classitems.name: createAppointment

params.name: options
params.description: An object containing options and stuff.

props.name: start
props.description: The start of the appointment, time is ignored when `options.fullDay` is set to true.

props.name: end
props.description: The end of the appointment, this is ignored when `options.fullDay` is set to true.

props.name: fullDay
props.description: When this is true, `options.end` is ignored and only `options.start` is used to set the begin and the end for the appointment.

props.name: location
props.description: The location (classroom for example) for the appointment.

props.name: content
props.description: Some random string of characters you want to save.

props.name: type
props.description: The type of the appointment: 1 for personal or 16 for planning
